data.description: Welcome to a fantastic property in Canal Winchester! This home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a generous 2500 square feet of living space. Stay warm on chilly nights with a cozy fireplace.Enjoy your own private oasis in the huge fenced-in yard - perfect for gatherings or quiet moments. Additional space is available with a full basement, offering endless possibilities for a home gym, game room, or more.This property is more than just a house; it's a haven ready for you to call home. If you're looking to upgrade your living situation, Schedule a showing today!
